Name: Meta Platforms Inc.
Description: Meta Platforms, Inc., headquartered in Menlo Park, California, is a dominant player in the technology sector, primarily recognized for its influential social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp. The company is aggressively investing in the development of virtual and augmented reality through its Reality Labs division, positioning itself at the forefront of the metaverse evolution. These strategic initiatives not only enhance user interaction within its expansive ecosystem but also bolster its robust advertising model, underscoring Meta's integral role in shaping the future of a rapidly evolving digital economy.
Address: 1 META WAY, MENLO PARK, CA, UNITED STATES, 94025
